1. *Zamolio* sam te da mi pomogneš. (I asked you to help me.)
2. Molim te, da me *zamoliš* da mu pomognem. (Please, ask me to help him.)
3. *Zamolila* me je da joj pozajmim novac. (She asked me to lend her money.)
4. Kada *zamolite* nekoga za uslugu, treba da mu se zahvalite. (When you ask someone for a favor, you should thank them.)
5. Molim te, da me *zamoliš* da ti pomognem sa ovim zadatkom. (Please, ask me to help you with this task.)
6. Kada bi me *zamolio*, rado bih ti pomogao. (If you asked me, I would gladly help you.)
7. *Zamolite* konobara da nam donese račun. (Ask the waiter to bring us the bill.)
8. Oni su me *zamolili* da im pomognem oko organizacije događaja. (They asked me to help them with the event organization.)
9. Bilo bi lepo kada bi me *zamolio* pre nego što uzmeš moj telefon. (It would be nice if you asked me before taking my phone.)
10. Kada bi me *zamolio* ranije, mogao sam ti pomoći. (If you had asked me earlier, I could have helped you.)